Package: indi-toupcam
Architecture: any
Depends: ${shlibs:Depends}, ${misc:Depends}, libindi1, libtoupcam
Description: INDI Driver for Toupcam cameras
 Driver for Toupcam cameras.
 .
 This driver is compatible with any INDI client such as KStars or Xephem.

Package: indi-toupcam-dbg
Priority: extra
Section: debug
Architecture: any
Depends: indi-toupcam (= ${binary:Version}), ${misc:Depends}
Description: INDI Driver for Toupcam cameras
 Driver for Toupcam cameras.
 .
 This driver is compatible with any INDI client such as KStars or Xephem.
 This package contains the debug symbols for the this driver, useful to investigate problems in INDI.
